## ğŸ“Œ Overview
FoodieExpress is a modern food delivery web application that connects users with local restaurants. It features a seamless ordering experience with restaurant browsing, menu viewing, and secure checkout.

## ğŸš€ Features

### Restaurant Discovery
- Browse restaurants by cuisine type
- View ratings and delivery times
- Search by name or location

### Order Management
- Add items to cart
- Customize orders
- Track order status

### User Experience
- Responsive design
- Secure authentication
- Order history

