## ğŸ Getting Started

### Prerequisites
- Node.js v16+
- PostgreSQL 12+
- npm or yarn

### Installation

1. Clone the repository:
```bash
git clone https://github.com/Raman071/Delivery-Website
cd foodie-express
Install backend dependencies:

bash
cd server
npm install
Install frontend dependencies:

bash
cd ../client
npm install
Running the App
Start the backend server:

bash
cd server
nodemon index.js
# or use regular node if you don't have nodemon
# node index.js
Start the frontend development server:

bash
cd ../client
npm start
Access the application:
Open http://localhost:3000 in your browser.
